snippet.title: The Lighthouse Alpha Demo - Reaction Reel
snippet.description:
We never knew doors and phones could be so scary

Thanks for playing :)

Check out all of the Awesome Youtuber's in this video here https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLbRvdDViMnhc3n58IOtoKRqY-cqJO-AzH  and watch their full play-through of the demo and don't forget to subscribe to them. They're awesome!

Support on Kickstarter: 
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/shadowknightsstudio/the-lighthouse-2?ref=user_menu

Steam Greenlight: 
https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=789625057

Download the Demo Here: http://www.indiedb.com/games/the-lighthouse1/downloads/the-lighthouse-alpha-demo-teaser

Have questions or feedback? Reach out to us at 
Support@ShadowKnightsStudio.com we would love to hear from you.
